OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny low cloud in parts of
OL,6,FDumfries and Galloway soon burning
OL,7,Foff. Then dry with some good sunny
OL,8,Fspells. Becoming very warm to hot,
OL,9,Fwith some cooling sea breezes..
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA very warm and sunny evening
OL,12,Fwill be followed by a dry night with
OL,13,Fsome clear spells. Winds remaining
OL,14,Flight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FAnother bright day with some
OL,17,Fsunshine a times and becoming hot away
OL,18,Ffrom sea breezes. Later there is a
OL,19,Fslight chance of some heavy showers in
OL,20,Feast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
