OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,6,Fcooler cloudier Saturday in east with
OL,7,Fbest of sun in Southwest. Cloudy start
OL,8,Fon Sunday then brightening up with
OL,9,Fsunny intervals. Monday dry and sunny
OL,10,Fand becoming warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
